    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.1",
      "en": "Ready to transform your infrastructure ? Get in touch with the Elemento team for expert guidance , technical support , or partnership opportunities . Learn about our team and values and explore our product offerings .",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.10",
      "en": "Free parking available By Train 5 min walk from Cuneo Station By Air 1 h from Torino Airport Multiple Ways to Get Help Choose the support option that works best for you",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.11",
      "en": "Comprehensive guides, tutorials, and API documentation to help you get started and troubleshoot issues.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.12",
      "en": "Join our community forum to connect with other users, share experiences, and get help from peers.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.13",
      "en": "Free webinars, training sessions, and certification programs to help your team master Elemento.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.14",
      "en": "Quick answers to common questions",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.15",
      "en": "You can start using Elemento immediately with our free trial. Most customers are up and running within 30 minutes . Our quick-start guide walks you through the entire setup process.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.16",
      "en": "We offer comprehensive support including 24/7 documentation , community forums, email support, and priority support for enterprise customers. Our support team has an average response time of under 2 hours.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.17",
      "en": "Yes! Elemento is designed to be self-hostable , giving you complete control over your infrastructure and data. You can deploy on your own servers, private cloud, or hybrid environments.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.18",
      "en": "Absolutely. Our enterprise team works closely with customers to develop custom solutions that meet specific requirements. We offer custom integrations, white-label solutions, and dedicated support.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.19",
      "en": "We support SOC 2 , ISO 27001 , GDPR , HIPAA , and other major compliance frameworks with built-in security features and audit trails.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.2",
      "en": "Whether you're looking to get started with Elemento , need technical support , or want to explore partnership opportunities , we're here to help. Learn about our technical capabilities and read our latest insights and updates .",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.20",
      "en": "Data privacy is built into our platform. You control where your data is stored and processed, with encryption at rest and in transit . We never access your data without explicit permission.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.21",
      "en": "Join hundreds of organizations that have revolutionized their cloud operations with Elemento. Learn about our company mission and explore our product solutions .",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.contact.p.3",
      "en": "We'll get in touch soon!",
      "it": "",
      "source": "contact.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
